flowchart LR
  A1[Mic Channels] --> B1[STFT / frame]
  B1 --> C1[PHAT weighting]
  C1 --> D1[SRP scan 0..360]
  D1 --> E1[Peak pick + smoothing]
  E1 --> F1[Steering angle]
  F1 --> G1[Beamform weights]
  G1 --> H1[Sum -> Focused audio]
  H1 --> I1[Denoise (optional)]
  I1 --> J1[Output mic stream]
